{"tid":1216194,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家有冇諗過report Facebook fake account?","createTime":"2019-06-13T09:20:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-25T14:15:38.000Z","uid":34130,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"093983e30a2def31f3c685bdbf016b91c624c119","tid":1216194,"uid":34130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T09:20:54.000Z","msg":"成日係Facebook 見到d垃圾三毛用fake account 去開grp、四圍留言，去抹黑成個遊行 抹黑一眾義士<br />\n<br />\n有冇諗過要維持Facebook 既乾淨清潔？努力舉報fake account <br />\n<br />\nFake accounts 特徵如下：<br />\n1. 無個人相/得啲寵物/食物等等，總之唔係自己嘅相<br />\n2. 無History，見個account 只係得上一年/上幾年嘅update<br />\n3. Like 過Share 過嘅全部都係Game / Game-like app 嘅Post<br />\n4. 個名完同人連唔上關係 e.g. Zz Relmn, Mm Gnt<br />\n<br />\n合付呢四個特徵，基本上已經九成成係假Account<br />\n<br />\n例如：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mf002HG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmf002HG.png&h=ab4503c1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uPMC4V2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuPMC4V2.png&h=09bbd1d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家有發現邊d fake account，記得post上黎比大家集下氣😊"},{"pid":"c1ad2bec8d3d41763ab00eab2c8f8533eff9249b","tid":1216194,"uid":34130,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T15:49:49.000Z","msg":"推到有人睇"},{"pid":"43cf845066ebd3d9f2ed9c594fc04f449f1831f9","tid":1216194,"uid":34130,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T00:18:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4e7fd469978cfc470797da4406a7461eef649d05","tid":1216194,"uid":34130,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T04:50:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e1aa57efd35f804708f41b8f28be060ae0b2354d","tid":1216194,"uid":215249,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T06:59:56.000Z","msg":"冇用 facebook幫五毛"},{"pid":"708fede59881d7f090d34652d69128bf292140f0","tid":1216194,"uid":34130,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e1aa57efd35f804708f41b8f28be060ae0b2354d","t